OL,3,CMinister says he won't play a part in
OL,4,Cstopping GP practises from going
OL,5,Cprivate
OL,7,FThey issued a vote of no confidence in
OL,8,FThe Heath Minister, and threatened to
OL,9,Fconsider working otuside the NHS - but
OL,10,FMike Nesbitt has now offered to
OL,11,Fnegotiate with GPs over their contract.
OL,13,FHowever, the minister warned he can't
OL,14,Fstop GPs from going private -
OL,15,Fsomething he insisted he won't play a
OL,16,Fpart in.
OL,18,FSpeaking to UTV's Health Correspondent
OL,19,FDeborah McAleese he said: "I have no
OL,20,Finterest in participating in anything
OL,21,Fthat would bring on a hybrid system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
