OL,10,F"And let's be clear, when they talk
OL,11,Fabout a hybrid system, they basically
OL,12,Fmean those who can afford to pay,
OL,13,Fpaying.
OL,15,F"That of course runs against the
OL,16,Ffundamental tenet of the National
OL,17,FHealth Service. So my interest is
OL,18,Ftrying to repair relationships with
OL,19,FGPs, because I know on a two-way
OL,20,Fstreet, we we need to restore trust
OL,21,Fand respect."
