OL,3,CMinister says he won't play a part in
OL,4,Cstopping GP practises from going
OL,5,Cprivate
OL,7,FThe minister continued to say that as
OL,8,FGP's are independent contractors,
OL,9,Fleaving him with no power to stop them
OL,10,Ffrom leaving the NHS if it is their
OL,11,Ffirm will.
OL,13,FGP's have been warning for some time
OL,14,Fthat the current model of primary care
OL,15,Fis broken, and that a new system is
OL,16,Fneeded potentially outside the health
OL,17,Fservice.
