OL,7,FMembers of this community group
OL,8,Fremember a different health service,
OL,9,Fwhere no one worried about the cost of
OL,10,Fgetting care, and that's the way they
OL,11,Fwant it to stay.
OL,13,FOne member said: "People are
OL,14,Fstruggling, and I don't think it'd be
OL,15,Ffair to ask them to pay private."
OL,17,FWhile another asked: "What about
OL,18,Fpeople who can't afford to pay? Where
OL,19,Fdo they go?"
