OL,7,FDr. O'Hagan also said that withdrawal
OL,8,Ffrom NHS work is avoidable if more
OL,9,Ffunding is invested in primary care.
OL,10,FBut with a health budget in trouble,
OL,11,Fcan the Minister end this feud?
OL,13,FHealth Minister, Mike Nesbitt
OL,14,Fcontinued: "So, I think I'm a friend
OL,15,Fof GPs, but I'm in a situation where I
OL,16,Fcan't deliver what they want.
